    "longBusinessSummary": "Savimex Corporation produces and sells wood products in Vietnam, Japan, the United States, and Europe. The company offers solid wood, upholstered, contemporary, classic, hospitality, and casino furniture, as well as kitchen cabinets. It also provides interior materials, such as hardware products, aluminum doors and windows, casework console tables, closet and utility shelves, countertops, custom cabinet accessories, exterior and interior wood doors, interior architectural wood and case works, lobby reception desks, lobby lounge caseworks, metal and glass panels at cabinet doors, plywood or MDF products, restroom vanities, wall papers, wood lockers and cabinets, and wood and metal shelves; and wood carvings, including crests, spindles, corbels, and moldings. In addition, the company offers supported products, including bedding products comprising pillows, blankets, duvets, curtains, carpets, slippers, and towels; kitchen products consisting of kitchen utensils, inox cookware, ceramic products, and storage items; and decoration products. Further, the company provides interior design and exporting various products. Savimex Corporation was founded in 1985 and is based in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
